The paper focuses on iris segmentation and localization using deep learning methods, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The proposed method also involves multi-task learning, which is a popular research area in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper uses iris datasets, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
